Dependencies
============

This project depends on SDL2.0 libraries. Run next command to install
depencencies:

$ sudo aptitude install libsdl2-2.0-0 libsdl2-dev

  - libsdl2-2.0-0   - SDL2 libraries
  - libsdl2-dev     - SDL2 headers (for development)


Building the project
====================

$ make


Running the project
===================

$ ./sdl2test


Cleaning the project
====================

$ make clean


HACKING
=======

API by category: https://wiki.libsdl.org/APIByCategory
API by name: https://wiki.libsdl.org/CategoryAPI
